layout.house_prompt: A dental office with a reception-waiting area, two exam rooms, an X-ray room, a corridor, and a bathroom. The reception-waiting area has a reception desk with a computer and three chairs. The first exam room has a dental chair and a cabinet. The second exam room has a dental chair and a sink. The X-ray room has an X-ray machine. The corridor has a bench. The bathroom has a toilet and a sink.

reception_waiting.text_description: A modern, clean, professional dental office reception-waiting area with a reception desk with a computer and three waiting chairs; bright, welcoming, hygienic finishes.

bathroom.text_description: A modern, clean dental office bathroom with a toilet and a sink; hygienic, easy-clean finishes.

corridor.text_description: A modern, clean dental office corridor with a bench; durable, easy-clean finishes and clear circulation.

exam_room.text_description: A modern, clean dental exam room with a dental chair and a cabinet; bright clinical lighting and easy-clean finishes.

exam_room_2.text_description: A modern, clean dental exam room with a dental chair and a sink; bright clinical lighting and easy-clean finishes.

xray_room.text_description: A modern, clean dental X-ray room with an X-ray machine; simple clinical layout with easy-clean finishes.
